Add the following to your settings.json:

   {
     "env": {
       "CLAUDE_CODE_EXPERIMENTAL_AGENT_TEAMS": "1"
     }
   }

Method 2 - Settings file: Set defaultMode in ~/.claude/settings.json.
   {
     "permissions": {
       "defaultMode": "bypassPermissions"
     }
   }

Setup: Add to ~/.claude/settings.json (global) or .claude/settings.json (per-project).
   {
     "permissions": {
       "allow": [
         "Bash(npm run *)",
         "Bash(git commit *)",
         "Bash(git diff *)",
         "Edit"
       ]
     }
   }
